See slide 2.  Not sure how i feel about defunding the police.  Too many angles. I think we should at least wait untill we’ve used the police to make all those sealed indictment arrests. Maybe defunding them is a trick to try to get off the hook!
Keep in mind, once they are defunded something worse may take their place!
Why don’t we start with no more speeding tickets and no more curb stomping and see how that goes.
